name: Jame's Minecraft Tips
body:
### Welcome to my Minecraft Tips page for kids.
![minecraft](http://www.chriscarlsonart.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/Minecraft-sword-1024x678.jpg)
My name is James and I am 7.
I started playing Minecraft this year and I enjoy it so much. I would like other kids my age to learn how to play Minecraft aswell.
